difficulty: Easy tasks have fewer contents in the table and the answer is almost the title in each column. Hard tasks have huge wide tables you have to navigate to see and each column has too many words.
format: I like tables that are narrow so I don't need to swipe left or right to navigate. Super wide tables are hard to fetch information from them.also tables with too many words are hard to read on phones.
comments: For two or three questions I thought I got the right answers but they're not in the choices so I had to skip instead.
